Koga Shuko/Unitron/Hades/Anubis:


Koga Shuko stopped outside of his base.  Pressing a button and speaking into 
his comm., the shields and other defenses stood down.

Koga Shuko, followed by Unitron, Hades, and Anubis, entered through an access 
hatch, the shields immediately going back up, and the other defenses 
reactivating less than a millisecond later.

The four Predacons got into a CR chamber each, letting modern technology 
begin on repairing their damaged bodies to as good as new.
